    "en": {
      "title": "Three youths kidnapped in a tipper",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "There has been an incident where three youths belonging to Vallipunam and Teravill areas were attacked in Gomba under Pudukudiripu area of \u200b\u200bMullaitivu district and they were abducted in a tipper and severely assaulted.",
        "This has happened to three youths who were reported to have assaulted a youth from Kallaru area during a clash between youth groups last week.",
        "Yesterday evening, while a group of youths were abducting three youths in a tipper, the tipper's tire burst after hitting a bridge in Vishwamadu area.",
        "Following this, they left the tipper vehicle at the spot and abducted the youth.",
        "Subsequently, when the Pudukudiripu police went to the spot, the youths involved in the abduction incident escaped from the tipper vehicle and rescued the three abducted youths. They have been admitted to Mullaitivu District Hospital.",
        "Pudukudiripu police are conducting investigations regarding the owner of the vehicle and the driver. (R)"
      ],
